{"id": 2706, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中你都留下了哪些“电子设备后遗症”？", "description": "比如说，游戏打多了看谁都有点像 NPC。（图片来自：iStock ©️roberuto ）", "record_count": 3136, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190102182009WVMHozp2hwBP6Ut3.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-10T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 322050, "content": "没有手机陪伴，都睡不着，尝试放下，却无法安眠", "image": "img/option/option/20190110163340cOX2HuVx8P31RtCE", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520509}, {"id": 322051, "content": "不带手机出门就会尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 322055, "content": "听人说话时候真想要字幕。特别是方言这种生肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528174}, {"id": 322056, "content": "去厕所拉屎不是先找纸巾，而是先找手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 322313, "content": "时不时要看一眼有没有消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555617}, {"id": 322058, "content": "不带手机出门没有安全感 生活中完全不能离开手机 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554424}, {"id": 322059, "content": "现在看纸质书，翻页的时候会忍不住点一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331552}, {"id": 322061, "content": "一碰手机就是半个小时起步，晚上直接就是到两点", "image": "img/option/option/20190110171306Y5Br7QAjfXP9oWNk", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552420}, {"id": 322317, "content": "用平板用多了，\n在大街上看到任何一个显示屏，\n都想上前用手指戳一戳", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781340}, {"id": 322318, "content": "总是在戳平板的时候把大拇指放在食指第二个关节上，放佛拿着apple pencil……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781340}, {"id": 322063, "content": "彩六玩多了看见摄像头就想打", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469196}, {"id": 322064, "content": "坐地铁不玩手机时，觉得我在和一群寄生虫一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549496}, {"id": 322065, "content": "出门必带耳机，尽管只去小区门口的超市。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384343}, {"id": 322321, "content": "即便是复习周也有超过一半的时间花在玩手机上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555762}, {"id": 322578, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518231}, {"id": 322579, "content": "塞尔达玩多了看见什么都想爬上去……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557514}, {"id": 322068, "content": "找不到的东西可能响一下会找到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519819}, {"id": 322070, "content": "手机开机，我开机。手机关机，我关机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184346}, {"id": 322071, "content": "手机除了睡觉，从不离身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457517}, {"id": 322072, "content": "没了弹幕的视频 就像没了番茄酱的薯条 毫无灵魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886727}, {"id": 322075, "content": "朋友圈点赞红点必看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 322076, "content": "冬天一到先担心手机会不会又冻死！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 322077, "content": "解锁，划两下，锁屏，舒服……\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484333}, {"id": 322590, "content": "刚关手机屏幕，立马又亮屏去看时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113677}, {"id": 322079, "content": "挤多了牙膏想按撤销键。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524833}, {"id": 322081, "content": "时刻带手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551772}, {"id": 322082, "content": "重度患者 连解手都要拿着手机 早晚有一天掉坑里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551060}, {"id": 322083, "content": "玩手机就像吸食鸦片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554520}, {"id": 322084, "content": "断网=休克", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551481}, {"id": 322085, "content": "在任何物品上看见小图片 就想撑开放大", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 34500}, {"id": 322086, "content": "即使不玩手机 也想要手机在自己的视线范围之类或者必须在兜里 ", "image": "img/option/option/20190110192108g2uCvpLxKIYTQE95.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554528}, {"id": 322090, "content": "没了手机，没有安全感，即使手机没有电，闲着没事的时候，就想打开看看，成为了必不可少的一部分，占据了太多位置", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554546}, {"id": 322095, "content": "手机是另一半，没了就丢了魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554555}, {"id": 320305, "content": "用惯了触屏设备，用起电脑来也想要摸屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320306, "content": "当某个人说话太啰嗦的时候忍不住想屏蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320307, "content": "电影院看节奏太慢的电影就很想摁快进／x2倍速", "image": null, "praise_count": 176, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 320308, "content": "看到很想吐槽的事情，就想点弹幕看看别人是怎么说的", "image": null, "praise_count": 368, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 326708, "content": "看电视想快进", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578925}, {"id": 322103, "content": "明明不想看无意义的弹幕，但是为了无意义中的那一抹搞笑弹幕，还是选择二刷的时候开弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554602}, {"id": 322106, "content": "有手机我不玩，但是没有手机就想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 322108, "content": "20多岁反而近视了，以前可是通过了飞行员体检的人……\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362771}, {"id": 322109, "content": "手机电量低于50％就觉得很没有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1545466}, {"id": 322111, "content": "点鼠标，点点点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 322115, "content": "随时害怕手机没电…没事就拿出来看一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554672}, {"id": 322117, "content": "路太远的时候就想闪现过去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335123}, {"id": 322119, "content": "离开了手机没有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525092}, {"id": 322120, "content": "没手机感觉空落落的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 322122, "content": "无聊的时候把手机里的app挨个翻一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514757}, {"id": 322124, "content": "眼睛酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552948}, {"id": 322125, "content": "干什么没手机就没安全感把", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554724}]}